[2026-03-18T12:08:52.998Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01W1PXBUxGLvKsp4LackoeoM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_013B328hZnVH9vSv52VXT8Qx","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"curl -s -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/ideas \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"scan_id\": \"d4eaed24-44dd-47f1-afe3-1b8702a903b2\",\n    \"project_id\": \"c6fd0474-19f1-4223-b6a9-752077c51d3d\",\n    \"scan_type\": \"tech_innovator\",\n    \"category\": \"performance\",\n    \"title\": \"Kafka-native event bus replacing SQLite poll loop\",\n    \"description\": \"The event processor is a 2s setInterval poll loop ported from the desktop Rust app (engine/background.rs). Each tick queries SQLite for pending events, then does O(events x matches) DB calls to load subscriptions, personas, tools, and concurrency counts. Kafka is already deployed for output/lifecycle but the event bus ignores it entirely. Move event ingestion onto Kafka: publishEvent() produces to persona.events.v1, a consumer group processes events with real-time dispatch, and SQLite becomes a materialized view for API queries only. Spike: Route publishEvent() through Kafka producer, add a consumer that calls matchEvent() and dispatch, benchmark latency vs poll loop. Risk: Kafka consumer lag could delay processing under burst; SQLite read-after-write consistency for API callers needs careful handling.\",\n    \"reasoning\": \"The 2s poll floor is a hard latency ceiling that no optimization within the current architecture can break. Moving to Kafka-native processing dissolves both the latency floor AND the N+1 query cascade, while unifying the system on one event backbone instead of two disconnected subsystems. This compounds: every future feature (chaining, content routing, fan-out) builds on the stream rather than fighting the poll loop.\",\n    \"effort\": 8,\n    \"impact\": 9,\n    \"risk\": 7\n  }'","description":"Submit idea 1: Kafka-native event bus"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":195,"cache_read_input_tokens":65848,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":195},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"782e4324-9122-4bd8-ac29-f35468e2642b","uuid":"7abdac8a-5e5d-4d6f-8bba-8dd5d078aef4"}
