[2026-03-18T12:09:42.534Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Cb9mu3WMp1ixBYQfNA7Az2","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 4 ideas submitted successfully. The DELETE endpoint returned HTML (likely a 404 for that route format), but no matter — all ideas are saved.\n\n## Summary\n\n**4 technology bet ideas** saved to Vibeman for the **Event Bus & Subscriptions** context:\n\n| # | Title | Category | Effort | Impact | Risk |\n|---|-------|----------|--------|--------|------|\n| 1 | **Kafka-native event bus replacing SQLite poll loop** | performance | 8 | 9 | 7 |\n| 2 | **Payload-aware subscription filters via JSONPath** | functionality | 7 | 9 | 6 |\n| 3 | **Persona-to-persona event chaining via Kafka bridge** | functionality | 7 | 10 | 8 |\n| 4 | **In-memory subscription routing table with hot reload** | performance | 7 | 9 | 6 |\n\n### Key Structural Constraints Identified\n\n1. **2s poll loop ceiling** — The `eventProcessor.ts` is a `setInterval` port from the desktop Rust app. It creates a hard latency floor AND an N+1 query cascade (O(events x matches) DB calls per tick). Kafka is already deployed but the event bus doesn't use it.\n\n2. **String-only event matching** — `matchEvent()` in `bus.ts` can only filter on `eventType` (exact) and `sourceFilter` (prefix wildcard). No payload-level routing means every GitLab webhook variant is indistinguishable, wasting expensive LLM executions on false-positive matches.\n\n3. **Disconnected event loop** — Personas emit events to Kafka (`dispatcher.ts:134`), the schema has a `chain` trigger type, but emitted events never re-enter the SQLite event bus. The infrastructure for agent chaining exists on both ends but the bridge is missing — this is the gap between \"script runner\" and \"agent orchestration platform.\""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5366,"cache_read_input_tokens":66043,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5366},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"782e4324-9122-4bd8-ac29-f35468e2642b","uuid":"20085b2e-8ad1-4cef-b09a-416e143ffddf"}
